---
// Componente: Cómo Funciona (Modernizado)
---

<section class="py-24 bg-transparent relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorative background element -->
  <div
    class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-gradient-to-b from-[#e6b866]/5 to-transparent rounded-full blur-3xl -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/3 pointer-events-none"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span
        class="inline-block py-1 px-3 rounded-full bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-sm font-sans font-medium mb-4 tracking-wide"
      >
        El Proceso Divino
      </span>
      <h2
        class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-slate-800 tracking-tight flex items-center justify-center gap-3"
      >
        <span>📚</span> Cómo funciona la calculadora
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Grid de Pasos -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-10">
      <!-- Paso 1 -->
      <div
        class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100/50 shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.04)] hover:shadow-[0_15px_40px_rgba(230,184,102,0.15)] hover:border-[#e6b866]/30 transition-all duration-500 overflow-hidden hover:-translate-y-1"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-slate-50/50 rounded-bl-full opacity-50 transform translate-x-16 -translate-y-16 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-[#e6b866]/5 transition-all duration-700"
        >
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div
            class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-white shadow-[0_2px_10px_rgba(0,0,0,0.03)] flex items-center justify-center text-xl border border-slate-100 font-serif font-medium text-[#e6b866]"
          >
            1
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3
              class="text-xl font-serif text-slate-800 mb-2 flex items-center gap-2"
            >
              📝 Completa tus datos sagrados
            </h3>
            <p
              class="text-slate-600 font-sans font-medium leading-relaxed text-sm"
            >
              Introduce tu nombre completo, apellidos, idioma materno y fecha de
              nacimiento con precisión. Cada letra y número tiene un valor
              sagrado en la Cábala.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Paso 2 -->
      <div
        class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100/50 shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.04)] hover:shadow-[0_15px_40px_rgba(230,184,102,0.15)] hover:border-[#e6b866]/30 transition-all duration-500 overflow-hidden hover:-translate-y-1"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-slate-50/50 rounded-bl-full opacity-50 transform translate-x-16 -translate-y-16 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-[#e6b866]/5 transition-all duration-700"
        >
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div
            class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-white shadow-[0_2px_10px_rgba(0,0,0,0.03)] flex items-center justify-center text-xl border border-slate-100 font-serif font-medium text-[#e6b866]"
          >
            2
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3
              class="text-xl font-serif text-slate-800 mb-2 flex items-center gap-2"
            >
              🧮 Cálculo automático
            </h3>
            <p
              class="text-slate-600 font-sans font-medium leading-relaxed text-sm"
            >
              El sistema aplica los valores numerológicos cabalísticos según tu
              idioma materno, usando las correspondencias tradicionales del
              Árbol de la Vida.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Paso 3 -->
      <div
        class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100/50 shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.04)] hover:shadow-[0_15px_40px_rgba(230,184,102,0.15)] hover:border-[#e6b866]/30 transition-all duration-500 overflow-hidden hover:-translate-y-1"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-slate-50/50 rounded-bl-full opacity-50 transform translate-x-16 -translate-y-16 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-[#e6b866]/5 transition-all duration-700"
        >
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div
            class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-white shadow-[0_2px_10px_rgba(0,0,0,0.03)] flex items-center justify-center text-xl border border-slate-100 font-serif font-medium text-[#e6b866]"
          >
            3
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3
              class="text-xl font-serif text-slate-800 mb-2 flex items-center gap-2"
            >
              🌳 Recibe tu mapa
            </h3>
            <p
              class="text-slate-600 font-sans font-medium leading-relaxed text-sm"
            >
              Obtén instantáneamente tu mapa numerológico básico con
              explicaciones claras basadas en las Sefirot y senderos
              cabalísticos.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Paso 4 -->
      <div
        class="group relative bg-[#FCFBF9] rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-[0_20px_40px_rgba(230,184,102,0.15)] transition-all duration-500 overflow-hidden hover:-translate-y-1"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-white rounded-bl-full opacity-50 transform translate-x-16 -translate-y-16 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700"
        >
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div
            class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-white shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center text-xl border border-slate-50 font-serif font-bold text-[#e6b866]"
          >
            4
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3
              class="text-xl font-serif text-slate-800 mb-2 flex items-center gap-2"
            >
              📖 Profundiza
            </h3>
            <p
              class="text-slate-600 font-sans font-medium leading-relaxed text-sm"
            >
              Explora nuestros recursos para una interpretación completa y
              transformadora basada en la tradición cabalística auténtica.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA Button -->
    <div class="mt-16 text-center">
      <a
        href="#calculador"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-10 py-4 bg-slate-900 text-white font-sans font-medium tracking-widest text-sm hover:bg-slate-800 transition-all duration-300 rounded shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-0.5"
      >
        🚀 DESCUBRELO AHORA
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
